text: A by-election was held for the New South Wales Legislative Assembly electorate of Parramatta on 27 August 1994 following the death of sitting member, Andrew Ziolkowski. The Labor candidate was his widow Gabrielle Harrison. ==Results== ==See also== *Electoral results for the district of Parramatta ==References== Category:1994 elections in Australia Category:New South Wales state by- elections Category:1990s in New South Wales
title: 1994 Parramatta state by-election
